find cost: int(1..10)
find carbon: int(1..10)

such that (cost + carbon) <= 15

dominance relation
    (cost <= fromSolution(cost)) /\
    (carbon <= fromSolution(carbon)) /\
    (
        (cost < fromSolution(cost)) \/
        (carbon < fromSolution(carbon))
    )

dominance relation
    (cost <= fromSolution(cost))
